data.description: Showings to start the week of 1/8/24.   New roof 10/2019--10/2019 new hot water heater, new electrical and plumbing, new appliances and fridge included, new windows throughout 2023.  Open floor plan with chef's kitchen--gas cooking, concrete counter tops, new cabinets, white subway tile. Laminate hard flooring throughout home, no carpet. large 1 car garage. Huge backyard backs up to an easement--perfect for family barbecues. Great location, across from Westwood Terrace Elementary in the NISD and shopping nearby
